despite flat sales, its profit rose 11 percent to $178.1 million in
the third quarter of its 1989 fiscal year compared with a year
earlier.
   The aerospace, automotive, electronics and graphics firm reported
earnings Wednesday of 70 cents a share for the period ended June 30.
